cuems-wsclient (0.2.1-1) UNRELEASED; urgency=medium

  * bridge: fix auto-load editor-success race that logged a false failure
    when the editor's project_ready ack returned before wait_engine's first
    sleep cycle (167868c). Three races in a row would have wrongly disabled
    auto-load for the session.
  * bridge: add controller_poweroff_cmd config field, optional split of the
    local controller's poweroff/reboot command from the SSH node command
    (f4c2304). Empty default preserves existing single-cmd behaviour; useful
    for safe testing when controller WoL-from-S5 is unreliable, and for
    maintenance reboots that should leave nodes powered off.
  * End-to-end verified against a real Shelly Pro 1 (`source: "timer"`
    proves hardware fired autonomously); SSH-fanout to slave_dev real
    (rc=0), reachability poll detected slave's network-down at +14s, then
    Shelly armed and local poweroff issued at +16s.

